> 	for (8 times) {
> 		ask user to type something
> 		for (i = 0; no_keypress; i++)
> 			;
> 		the low-order value of "i" is probably quite random now
> 	}

        That looks good - mind if I keep it? OTOH I found a good
        one of these in the source code for PGP 2.0

